{"tid":1850543,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"入u後好焦慮好抑鬱","createTime":"2020-01-29T14:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T13:06:18.000Z","uid":346941,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a2c1c4ac5217eea668b980a704a2704847af879d","tid":1850543,"uid":346941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T14:56:02.000Z","msg":"入u之後真係好焦慮，又唔知點解<br />\n其實潛意識知道自己好幸福，生活要咩有咩，表面上好似好開心好多朋友好多人鍾意，但我知道全部都係假象<br />\n大學扮到好social，但自己yo完人又唔會好enjoy，其實本質上根本就係內向毒撚<br />\n群埋一班人，佢地根本唔care成績，成日掛住玩，我又唔想自己唔合群，就同佢地一齊玩到爛曬gpa<br />\n我呢家知錯，想遠離佢地，想改過自新，但係已經錯得太多<br />\n所以我忍唔住想逃避現實<br />\n我知道我咁樣落去唔得，但我不顧後果咁將所有嘢postpone，就係可以俾時間自己摺係屋企，一的起心肝想改變就又忍唔住procrastinate<br />\n好撚失敗啊我<br />\n見到大學啲人個個又有拖排又有返工又兼顧到成績過3爆4<br />\n我真係覺得自己咩都唔係<br />\n唉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce13e3acb49c3d6f3156e81a2f3107cd00631215","tid":1850543,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T14:57:04.000Z","msg":"樓豬係毒撚?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"519227a21a8451c316983be83033dfdc18760ba1","tid":1850543,"uid":346941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce13e3acb49c3d6f3156e81a2f3107cd00631215","tid":1850543,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T14:57:04.000Z","msg":"樓豬係毒撚?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T15:00:51.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />毒撚做咩都有錯"},{"pid":"56fe333a99336f34c142eec0fdd9bcb79bb6ad0a","tid":1850543,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T15:00:54.000Z","msg":"樓豬係毒撚?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aafdeec8a5ac983830cc6eb908171348cdd4f9e9","tid":1850543,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T15:02:15.000Z","